channel.title: Project Insanity [Revision 83] Current OSRS
channel.description:
Not much will be posted currently since the project has just been started. Basically I am converting Project Insanity to current osrs so you guys can actually use the real client and no more of this 317 with osrs data stuff. I do not care if this is dumb or pointless I am doing this to learn about the current osrs information since they are starting to change a lot of information. I will be releasing this when I am done to the public and I do not plan on selling it.
I will be making this thread better but basically this is just to show you guys the progress that is moving along.
